v4W.ENko - "IAM-08_CPP-05_S-73".

[Intermediate Algorithmic Multicomponent]
[COLOR Practice with Patterns] [Statics] 
Background color domination [slow color side] - Black. 
The artwork connects intermediate cross-pattern`s instructions to demonstrate the multicomponent relationship of various geometric algorithms. The abstraction is dedicated to the "Metaball", "Voronoi diagram" and "Delaunay triangulation" transformations. The patterns are linked in specific way to draw the algorithmic abstract artwork with each other. The energy of abstract processes in relationship of algorithms is linked inside. The whole visualizations is forming the abstract static image PNG 2608*4096 px.
